comments.body:
```sql
postgres=# select interval '13.123456789 seconds';
    interval
-----------------
 00:00:13.123457
(1 row)

postgres=# select interval '-13.123456789 seconds';
     interval
------------------
 -00:00:13.123457
(1 row)
```

this case is different from PG

 interval

(1 row)
